cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image processing and object detection using deep convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an automatic method for ColorChecker detection, which involves machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning models for object detection and recognition. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D models of the ColorChecker and their rendering in synthetic images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with color standards used in photography and filmmaking.
